Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_rx::_frm_max

AGL_GMX_RX_FRM_MAX = Frame Max length

Notes: When changing the LEN field, be sure that LEN does not exceed AGL_GMX_RX_JABBER[CNT]. Failure to meet this constraint will cause packets that are within the maximum length parameter to be rejected because they exceed the AGL_GMX_RX_JABBER[CNT] limit.

Notes:

Additionally reset when MIX<prt>_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
